leted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 441948, "reply_to": 2301747, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 1/3概率碰到摩托在1min圈，2/3概率碰到摩托在2min圈", "timestamp": 1629221953, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2301762, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441948, "reply_to": 2301755, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 为什么慢速概率更大呢，不太理解", "timestamp": 1629221963, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2301765, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 441948, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "谢谢dz的问题 有意思的", "timestamp": 1629221985, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2301769, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 441948, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不妨就三分钟，1分钟和3分钟时这车经过p点，人在0到3随机来等车，按占比均值一下就可以了，如Eve所说", "timestamp": 1629222025, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2301771, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 441948, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你要愿意积分也可以", "timestamp": 1629222049, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2301781, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441948, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "懂了，谢谢ABCDE诸君😄", "timestamp": 1629222219, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2303442, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 441948, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一个概率是调整机会的概率，一个概率是在时间上的概率。\n求等待摩托时间的期望值，首先要知道速度在时间上的分布。所以需要把在机会上的概率转换为在时间上的概率分布。\n时间上的速度概率分布为：\n1/3    2/3\n1         2\n也就是1/3的时间是低速状态。\n则等待时间期望值 = (1/3 * 1 + 2/3 * 2) * 0.5 = 5/6。", "timestamp": 1629260500, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2303448, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441948, "reply_to": 2303442, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 懂了，把机会转化成时间很重要，感谢F君", "timestamp": 1629260573, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2303455, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 441948, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "感觉我说的可能不准确，但这里的确涉及到一个概率分布的转换。", "timestamp": 1629260627, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2303468, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441948, "reply_to": 2303455, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 其实我看了前面各位的讲解之后想的也是最后要转化到时间上来，不然就会得出等可能遇到快速和慢速的结论", "timestamp": 1629260722, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 8, "pid": 441948, "reply": 19, "tag": null, "text": "#深夜动脑\n\n一辆摩托车绕操场开，每次经过p点后调整速度，有50%概率1分钟绕一圈，50%概率2分钟绕一圈，小明在任一时刻来到p点，求等待摩托时间的期望值", "timestamp": 1629221332, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1629260724, "url": "", "vote": {}}}